<title>USA: Torchmark investors pave way for split.</title>
<headline>Torchmark investors pave way for split.</headline>
<dateline>BIRMINGHAM, Ala. 1997-06-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Torchmark Corp said on Monday that its shareholders had voted to increase the amount of the company's total authorized common stock.</p>
<p>In May, when Torchmark announced the proposed increase, it said the authorization would clear the way for a two-for-one stock split.</p>
<p>In keeping with the previous announcement, Torchmark also set a 100 percent stock dividend on its common stock, payable on August 1, to its holders of record on July 1.</p>
